POLIOMYELITIS UPDATE (18): GLOBAL (WILD POLIOVIRUS TYPE 1, CIRCULATING VACCINE DERIVED POLIOVIRUS TYPES 1 AND 2), PAKISTAN VIOLENCE
***********************************************************************************************************************************
